  Recommended Reading and Audibles on Bitcoin

Bitcoin Whitepaper by Satoshi Nakamoto
  
21 Lessons: What I've Learned from Falling Down the Bitcoin Rabbit Hole by Gigi

Bitcoin Billionaires: A True Story of Genius, Betrayal, and Redemption by Ben Mezrich, Will Damron, et al.

Bitcoin: Independence reimagined by Knut Svanholm

Bitcoin: Sovereignty through mathematics by Knut Svanholm

Internet of Money Volume One: A Collection of Talks by Andreas Antonopoulos

Internet of Money Volume Two: A Collection of Talks by Andreas Antonopoulos

Internet of Money Volume Three: A Collection of Talks by Andreas Antonopoulos

KEYS TO BITCOIN: Understanding the Technology of Digital Money by Raphael Meyer

Mastering Bitcoin: Programming the Open Blockchain by Andreas Antonopoulos (also on GitHub)

My First Guide To Bitcoin: An Easy Read On The Cryptic Topic by Andrew O'Neil

Shelling Out: The Origins of Money by Nick Szabo

The Bitcoin Standard by Saifedean Ammous

The Little Bitcoin Book: Why Bitcoin Matters for Your Freedom, Finances, and Future by Bitcoin Collective

BITCOIN-Hard Money You Can't F*ck With by Jason A. Williams 
